final code changes for 1.0 alpha build

final code changes for 1.0 alpha build

Version 1.01

Added Apache License to source files. Updated About Activity page.

version 1.02 checkin

metered network setting tweaked. (Because my phone believes it to be a
metered wifi network).

1.0.3 changes

Progress bar shows download buffering. MediaPlayer released when left
too long paused in the background. About page cleaned up. Allow phone
calls and other notifications to mute music.

Song title display-initial meta classes and UI

Added the initial set of meta classes (but not the proxy code yet),
replaced PeriodicTimer with CountDownTimer.  Removed android support
library. Some View and Presenter class changes to support metadata.

Song titles are working

Song titles are working - some refinements may be needed. Code review
everything again. Evaluate if MetaStreamProxy can be just a single
thread instead of two. Evalulate if startService is an appropriate way
to update the song title.

Near ready for release update

Near ready for release update
Added preferences support for disabling metadata proxy

Lots of little fixes for metaproxy

IPv6 loopback socket support.  Change connection/read timeouts.
UrlEncode the embedded URL into the metaproxy.  Restart live streams on
disconnect. If we fail to initialize the proxy, fallback to normal
streaming.

Ship it!

Ready to ship version 1.09.
